## Verification Plan

### Automated Verification
- Verify that backend code compiles and tests pass (if any).
- Run server and check requests.

### Manual Verification
- Log in as the System Admin (default: `admin@hirelyft.in`, company: `Hirelyft India Pvt. Ltd.`).
- Verify that on the dashboard, only Hirelyft employees are shown.
- Go to "Companies Admin" and view the list of registered companies. Check that we see each company's admin list, total teams count, manager count, team leaders count, and employee count.
- Go to "Employees" and verify only Hirelyft employees are listed.
- Go to "Leave Requests" and verify only Hirelyft leave applications are displayed.
- Go to "Marketing Tracker" and verify only Hirelyft marketing employees are trackable.
- Log in as a Company Admin from another company and verify that they can only access their own company's employees, teams, leaves, etc., and cannot access the Companies Admin tab.
